#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.13"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.13:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.13:0.2"
msgid "2. Sāraṇīyavagga"
msgstr "2. Warm-hearted"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.13:0.3"
msgid "13. Nissāraṇīyasutta"
msgstr "13. Elements of Escape"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli3.291"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.13:1.1"
msgid "“Chayimā, bhikkhave, nissāraṇīyā dhātuyo."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these six elements of escape."

msgctxt "an6.13:1.2"
msgid "Katamā cha?"
msgstr "What six?"

msgctxt "an6.13:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "Take a mendicant who says:"

msgctxt "an6.13:1.4"
msgid ""
"‘mettā hi kho me cetovimutti bhāvitā bahulīkatā yānīkatā vatthukatā "
"anuṭṭhitā paricitā susamāraddhā;"
msgstr ""
"‘I’ve developed the heart’s release by love. I’ve cultivated it, made it my "
"vehicle and my basis, kept it up, consolidated it, and properly implemented "
"it."

msgctxt "an6.13:1.5"
msgid "atha ca pana me byāpādo cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhatī’ti."
msgstr "Yet somehow ill will still occupies my mind.’"

msgctxt "an6.13:1.6"
msgid ""
"So ‘mā hevan’tissa vacanīyo: ‘māyasmā evaṃ avaca; mā bhagavantaṃ "
"abbhācikkhi, na hi sādhu bhagavato abbhakkhānaṃ, na hi bhagavā evaṃ vadeyya."
msgstr ""
"They should be told, ‘Not so, venerable! Don’t say that. Don’t misrepresent "
"the Buddha, for misrepresentation of the Buddha is not good. And the Buddha "
"would not say that."

msgctxt "an6.13:1.7"
msgid ""
"Aṭṭhānametaṃ, āvuso, anavakāso yaṃ mettāya cetovimuttiyā bhāvitāya "
"bahulīkatāya yānīkatāya vatthukatāya anuṭṭhitāya paricitāya susamāraddhāya; "
msgstr ""
"It’s impossible, reverend, it cannot happen that the heart’s release by love "
"has been developed and properly implemented, "

#. VAR: ṭhassati → ṭhassatīti (sabbattha)
msgctxt "an6.13:1.8"
msgid ""
"atha ca panassa byāpādo cittaṃ pariyādāya ṭhassati, netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr "yet somehow ill will still occupies the mind."

#. VAR: byāpādassa yadidaṃ mettācetovimuttī’ti → mettācetovimutti (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an6.13:1.9"
msgid "Nissaraṇañhetaṃ, āvuso, byāpādassa yadidaṃ mettācetovimuttī’ti. (1)"
msgstr ""
"For it is the heart’s release by love that is the escape from ill will.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.13:2.1"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "Take another mendicant who says:"

msgctxt "an6.13:2.2"
msgid ""
"‘karuṇā hi kho me cetovimutti bhāvitā bahulīkatā yānīkatā vatthukatā "
"anuṭṭhitā paricitā susamāraddhā; "
msgstr ""
"‘I’ve developed the heart’s release by compassion. I’ve cultivated it, made "
"it my vehicle and my basis, kept it up, consolidated it, and properly "
"implemented it. "

msgctxt "an6.13:2.3"
msgid "atha ca pana me vihesā cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhatī’ti."
msgstr "Yet somehow the thought of harming still occupies my mind.’"

msgctxt "an6.13:2.4"
msgid ""
"So ‘mā hevan’tissa vacanīyo: ‘māyasmā evaṃ avaca; mā bhagavantaṃ "
"abbhācikkhi, na hi sādhu bhagavato abbhakkhānaṃ, na hi bhagavā evaṃ vadeyya."
msgstr "They should be told, ‘Not so, venerable! …"

msgctxt "an6.13:2.5"
msgid ""
"Aṭṭhānametaṃ, āvuso, anavakāso yaṃ karuṇāya cetovimuttiyā bhāvitāya "
"bahulīkatāya yānīkatāya vatthukatāya anuṭṭhitāya paricitāya susamāraddhāya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.13:2.6"
msgid ""
"atha ca panassa vihesā cittaṃ pariyādāya ṭhassati, netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.13:2.7"
msgid "Nissaraṇañhetaṃ, āvuso, vihesāya yadidaṃ karuṇācetovimuttī’ti. (2)"
msgstr ""
"For it is the heart’s release by compassion that is the escape from thoughts "
"of harming.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an6.13:3.1"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "Take another mendicant who says:"

msgctxt "an6.13:3.2"
msgid ""
"‘muditā hi kho me cetovimutti bhāvitā bahulīkatā yānīkatā vatthukatā "
"anuṭṭhitā paricitā susamāraddhā;"
msgstr ""
"‘I’ve developed the heart’s release by rejoicing. I’ve cultivated it, made "
"it my vehicle and my basis, kept it up, consolidated it, and properly "
"implemented it."

# BB’s “discontent” doesn’t work in this context.
msgctxt "an6.13:3.3"
msgid "atha ca pana me arati cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhatī’ti."
msgstr "Yet somehow negativity still occupies my mind.’"

msgctxt "an6.13:3.4"
msgid ""
"So ‘mā hevan’tissa vacanīyo: ‘māyasmā evaṃ avaca; mā bhagavantaṃ "
"abbhācikkhi, na hi sādhu bhagavato abbhakkhānaṃ, na hi bhagavā evaṃ vadeyya."
msgstr "They should be told, ‘Not so, venerable! …"

msgctxt "an6.13:3.5"
msgid ""
"Aṭṭhānametaṃ, āvuso, anavakāso yaṃ muditāya cetovimuttiyā bhāvitāya "
"bahulīkatāya yānīkatāya vatthukatāya anuṭṭhitāya paricitāya susamāraddhāya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.13:3.6"
msgid "atha ca panassa arati cittaṃ pariyādāya ṭhassati, netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.13:3.7"
msgid "Nissaraṇañhetaṃ, āvuso, aratiyā yadidaṃ muditācetovimuttī’ti. (3)"
msgstr ""
"For it is the heart’s release by rejoicing that is the escape from "
"negativity.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli3.292"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an6.13:4.1"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "Take another mendicant who says:"

msgctxt "an6.13:4.2"
msgid ""
"‘upekkhā hi kho me cetovimutti bhāvitā bahulīkatā yānīkatā vatthukatā "
"anuṭṭhitā paricitā susamāraddhā;"
msgstr ""
"‘I’ve developed the heart’s release by equanimity. I’ve cultivated it, made "
"it my vehicle and my basis, kept it up, consolidated it, and properly "
"implemented it."

msgctxt "an6.13:4.3"
msgid "atha ca pana me rāgo cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhatī’ti."
msgstr "Yet somehow desire still occupies my mind.’"

msgctxt "an6.13:4.4"
msgid ""
"So ‘mā hevan’tissa vacanīyo: ‘māyasmā evaṃ avaca; mā bhagavantaṃ "
"abbhācikkhi, na hi sādhu bhagavato abbhakkhānaṃ, na hi bhagavā evaṃ vadeyya."
msgstr "They should be told, ‘Not so, venerable! …"

msgctxt "an6.13:4.5"
msgid ""
"Aṭṭhānametaṃ, āvuso, anavakāso yaṃ upekkhāya cetovimuttiyā bhāvitāya "
"bahulīkatāya yānīkatāya vatthukatāya anuṭṭhitāya paricitāya susamāraddhāya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.13:4.6"
msgid "atha ca panassa rāgo cittaṃ pariyādāya ṭhassati, netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.13:4.7"
msgid "Nissaraṇañhetaṃ, āvuso, rāgassa yadidaṃ upekkhācetovimuttī’ti. (4)"
msgstr ""
"For it is the heart’s release by equanimity that is the escape from desire.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an6.13:5.1"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "Take another mendicant who says:"

msgctxt "an6.13:5.2"
msgid ""
"‘animittā hi kho me cetovimutti bhāvitā bahulīkatā yānīkatā vatthukatā "
"anuṭṭhitā paricitā susamāraddhā;"
msgstr ""
"‘I’ve developed the signless release of the heart. I’ve cultivated it, made "
"it my vehicle and my basis, kept it up, consolidated it, and properly "
"implemented it."

msgctxt "an6.13:5.3"
msgid "atha ca pana me nimittānusāri viññāṇaṃ hotī’ti."
msgstr "Yet somehow my consciousness still follows after signs.’"

msgctxt "an6.13:5.4"
msgid ""
"So ‘mā hevan’tissa vacanīyo: ‘māyasmā evaṃ avaca; mā bhagavantaṃ "
"abbhācikkhi, na hi sādhu bhagavato abbhakkhānaṃ, na hi bhagavā evaṃ vadeyya."
msgstr "They should be told, ‘Not so, venerable! …"

msgctxt "an6.13:5.5"
msgid ""
"Aṭṭhānametaṃ, āvuso, anavakāso yaṃ animittāya cetovimuttiyā bhāvitāya "
"bahulīkatāya yānīkatāya vatthukatāya anuṭṭhitāya paricitāya susamāraddhāya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.13:5.6"
msgid ""
"atha ca panassa nimittānusāri viññāṇaṃ bhavissati, netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.13:5.7"
msgid ""
"Nissaraṇañhetaṃ, āvuso, sabbanimittānaṃ yadidaṃ animittācetovimuttī’ti. (5)"
msgstr ""
"For it is the signless release of the heart that is the escape from all "
"signs.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an6.13:6.1"
msgid "Idha pana bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "Take another mendicant who says:"

# ASmiti is a basic-level assumption, a fundamental construct of the mind based on identity. It’s not just a thought or idea. Which is pretty much the point of the difference between asmiti and sakkayaditthi.
#. VAR: vigataṃ → vigate (s1-3)
msgctxt "an6.13:6.2"
msgid "‘asmīti kho me vigataṃ, ayamahamasmīti ca na samanupassāmi;"
msgstr ""
"‘I’m rid of the conceit “I am”. And I don’t regard anything as “I am this”."

msgctxt "an6.13:6.3"
msgid ""
"atha ca pana me vicikicchākathaṃkathāsallaṃ cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhatī’ti."
msgstr "Yet somehow the dart of doubt and indecision still occupies my mind.’"

msgctxt "an6.13:6.4"
msgid ""
"So ‘mā hevan’tissa vacanīyo: ‘māyasmā evaṃ avaca; mā bhagavantaṃ "
"abbhācikkhi, na hi sādhu bhagavato abbhakkhānaṃ, na hi bhagavā evaṃ vadeyya."
msgstr ""
"They should be told, ‘Not so, venerable! Don’t say that. Don’t misrepresent "
"the Buddha, for misrepresentation of the Buddha is not good. And the Buddha "
"would not say that."

msgctxt "an6.13:6.5"
msgid ""
"Aṭṭhānametaṃ, āvuso, anavakāso yaṃ asmīti vigate ayamahamasmīti ca na "
"samanupassato;"
msgstr ""
"It’s impossible, reverend, it cannot happen that the conceit “I am” has been "
"done away with, and nothing is regarded as “I am this”,"

msgctxt "an6.13:6.6"
msgid ""
"atha ca panassa vicikicchākathaṃkathāsallaṃ cittaṃ pariyādāya ṭhassati, "
"netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr "yet somehow the dart of doubt and indecision still occupies the mind."

msgctxt "an6.13:6.7"
msgid ""
"Nissaraṇañhetaṃ, āvuso, vicikicchākathaṃkathāsallassa yadidaṃ asmīti "
"mānasamugghāto’ti. (6)"
msgstr ""
"For it is the uprooting of the conceit “I am” that is the escape from the "
"dart of doubt and indecision.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an6.13:7.1"
msgid "Imā kho, bhikkhave, cha nissāraṇīyā dhātuyo”ti."
msgstr "These are the six elements of escape.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.13:7.2"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
